Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.53,0:00:04.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,櫻花綻放之未來戀夢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.51,0:00:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天空好藍 你露出了微笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.25,0:00:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不經意的一句話使內心相繫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:29.32,0:00:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛穿上的鞋  敞開門扉的後方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:36.97,0:00:44.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟你重合的景色使我心動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:46.98,0:00:54.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,櫻花綻放之未來戀夢\N加速的心跳無法壓抑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:54.85,0:01:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兩人共同感受  季節不斷更替
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:02.39,0:01:10.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無可取代的瞬間\N編織著邂逅的物語
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.33,0:01:17.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對紛飛的櫻花許下心願
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.34,0:01:19.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向前行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.24,0:01:23.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,花盛開著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.03,0:01:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,琴梨？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.10,0:01:48.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我正在看琴梨的夢境嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.24,0:01:56.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無論是爸爸媽媽或姊姊的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.45,0:01:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我完全不知道他們的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.75,0:02:01.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.85,0:02:05.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們都是我第一次見到的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.22,0:02:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第一次見到的人？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.57,0:02:20.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,#23 真誠的告白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.21,0:02:26.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是令人難受的夢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.72,0:02:37.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.16,0:02:41.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我出門囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.03,0:02:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音夢，再一下子就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.47,0:03:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.25,0:03:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安  小智、小美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.05,0:03:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有看到新聞嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.15,0:03:45.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,初音島的櫻花原來很有名呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.42,0:03:49.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根據知名學者所說\N櫻花枯萎的原因還是個謎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.49,0:03:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.50,0:03:57.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,琴梨？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.23,0:03:58.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.67,0:04:00.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.00,0:04:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還有事，先走囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.28,0:04:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,琴梨她怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.81,0:04:11.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她最近怪怪的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.32,0:04:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對我而言那是我活下去的支柱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.72,0:04:22.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聆聽他人的心聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.29,0:04:25.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這像是一種心電感應
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.63,0:04:32.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要能知道對方的心思跟願望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.23,0:04:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做人處事就可以相當的圓滑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.81,0:04:40.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛開始以為是自己多心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.08,0:04:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我慢慢、慢慢地\N聽不見別人內心的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.95,0:04:53.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我相信等到明天\N一定能恢復成以前的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.82,0:04:57.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但卻是沒能實現的心願
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.10,0:05:03.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有時我覺得很礙事的這種能力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.83,0:05:08.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在失去之後才發現它的重要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.42,0:05:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.55,0:05:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,意思就是自然的演變
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.69,0:05:29.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,關於自發性的助動詞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.56,0:05:35.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,包含想、想起來\N擔心 忍耐 反省 感覺等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.00,0:05:38.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很多跟內心有關的動詞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.09,0:06:05.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無法聽到對方心聲的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.03,0:06:08.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該如何跟大家相處才好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.83,0:06:13.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我好害怕面對這件事實
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.04,0:06:21.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又遲到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.55,0:06:31.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朝倉同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.86,0:06:34.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,琴梨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.19,0:06:40.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.93,0:06:45.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,琴梨會蹺課真是稀奇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.93,0:06:46.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我聽到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.77,0:06:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,待在這裡可是會感冒的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.44,0:06:56.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朝倉同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.59,0:07:10.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,琴…梨？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.09,0:07:14.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我聽得見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.60,0:07:23.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我出門了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.47,0:07:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,琴梨？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.68,0:07:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,午安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.55,0:07:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是早安吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.68,0:07:35.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.55,0:07:37.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.69,0:07:43.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,後來很不可思議的是\N我只聽得到朝倉內心的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.83,0:07:50.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要能理解他人我就能安心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.93,0:07:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我跟朝倉在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.57,0:07:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,標題是"學園的太陽再度昇起"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.27,0:08:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是非正式新聞社的號外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.71,0:08:06.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過報導會根據你的回答修正
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.21,0:08:09.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還是一樣說話拐彎抹角的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.08,0:08:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽說白河琴梨的復活跟你有關
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.09,0:08:17.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果這是事實就會換成\N「發現朝倉哥哥劈腿」的這個標題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.29,0:08:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絕無此事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.86,0:08:22.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎，原來我也會搞錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.36,0:08:23.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朝倉同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.10,0:08:26.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,琴梨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.87,0:08:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的絕無此事嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.04,0:08:31.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還真煩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.17,0:08:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請吃吧，我不小心買太多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.45,0:08:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是炒麵麵包，真幸運
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.05,0:08:44.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.16,0:08:54.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實是想跟朝倉一起用餐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.33,0:09:01.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得跟朝倉在一起就好輕鬆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.31,0:09:08.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是因為輕鬆嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.35,0:09:14.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要能理解他人我就能安心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.75,0:09:17.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才會跟朝倉在一起嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.60,0:09:29.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的只是因為這樣嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.84,0:09:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是因為這樣…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.87,0:09:43.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不對，我跟朝倉不是那種關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.28,0:09:48.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼說呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.28,0:09:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟他在一起就覺得很輕鬆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.75,0:09:54.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在一起就能輕鬆是好事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.86,0:09:57.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然符合傳聞所說的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.93,0:10:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最近的琴梨變得很有精神了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.77,0:10:08.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是因為跟朝倉很親近的關係嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.14,0:10:09.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很親近？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.28,0:10:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請妳陪我真是抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.95,0:10:23.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請不用介意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.29,0:10:27.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也剛好要去買晚餐的材料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.12,0:10:30.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳會做菜啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.79,0:10:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊她…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.79,0:10:35.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為曆老師今天也開會到很晚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.16,0:10:39.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,琴梨會是個好太太呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.31,0:10:47.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最近的琴梨變得很有精神了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.71,0:10:50.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是因為跟朝倉很親近的關係嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.65,0:10:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很親近？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.58,0:10:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟他告白吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.42,0:10:56.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告白？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.43,0:11:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是因為在一起就能輕鬆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.43,0:11:10.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不是因為\N聽得到他的想法所以安心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.33,0:11:15.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是因為喜歡朝倉\N才想跟他在一起的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.08,0:11:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡朝倉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.75,0:11:34.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朝倉有沒有喜歡的人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.32,0:11:39.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他對我有什麼感覺呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.83,0:11:45.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好想知道朝倉的內心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.36,0:12:12.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,琴梨？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.53,0:12:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,琴梨，妳還好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.81,0:12:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都聽不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.75,0:12:36.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連朝倉的內心也…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.09,0:12:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽不到了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.60,0:12:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽得見別人的心聲？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.57,0:13:00.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳真的有這種能力嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.91,0:13:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.58,0:13:08.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說是心電感應或許比較好懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.22,0:13:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對我而言這種能力相當方便
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.92,0:13:18.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要能知道對方的心思跟願望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.96,0:13:20.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做人處事就可以相當的圓滑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.33,0:13:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能理解的話就可以很輕鬆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.20,0:13:34.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是現在我什麼都聽不見\N什麼都不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.75,0:13:42.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我好害怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.62,0:13:46.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之後我要怎麼活下去呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.62,0:13:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（無論如何都不會給你的）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.23,0:13:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可以讓你這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.63,0:13:56.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看我的攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.28,0:14:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.28,0:14:18.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼說呢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.39,0:14:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,琴梨，打起精神吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.16,0:14:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣不太負責任呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.63,0:14:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是別打起精神好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.00,0:14:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣也很不負責任呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.66,0:14:57.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我聽不見別人的心聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.93,0:15:02.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無法理解琴梨妳的不安與害怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.47,0:15:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能我不太會表達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.17,0:15:19.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為一點小事吵架\N或是後悔跟悲傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.68,0:15:27.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無法瞭解對方內心或許不方便
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.22,0:15:31.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.46,0:15:34.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我有很多事情不懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.76,0:15:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使是吵架
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.43,0:15:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也是有它的樂趣在呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.02,0:16:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.50,0:16:14.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在可以陪我一下嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.68,0:16:34.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實我並不是白河家的小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.29,0:16:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被白河家收養的我\N不能被人討厭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.53,0:16:46.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之必須讓大家喜歡我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.17,0:16:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每次哭泣我都會對這棵樹許願
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.64,0:16:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望能知道對方在想什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.51,0:17:00.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣在某一天\N我忽然聽得到他人的心聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.65,0:17:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和家人也能相處得很好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.39,0:17:08.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.49,0:17:15.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那場夢是這麼一回事嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.60,0:17:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當時的心願傳達給櫻花…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.04,0:17:27.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你，我已經不要緊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.02,0:17:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經不要緊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.84,0:18:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拂動小小花蕾的光芒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.65,0:18:20.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,閉上眼睛悄悄許下心願
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.53,0:18:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無法化為言語的思念\N讓我感覺好難過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.28,0:18:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以讓你看到真正的我嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.19,0:18:57.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,宛如與風兒齊聲歌唱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.36,0:19:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若是能陪你一起翱翔各地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.58,0:19:12.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那該有多好  天空真是美麗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.61,0:19:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,風的呢喃使我露出微笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.38,0:19:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望總有一天能傳達這份心意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.26,0:20:07.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結果我只是依賴這個能力\N完全沒有任何的進步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.87,0:20:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.08,0:20:16.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朝倉同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.45,0:20:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉讓你擔心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.88,0:20:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我又沒有做什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.79,0:20:28.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朝倉同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.09,0:20:33.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最初第一步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.90,0:20:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朝倉同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.64,0:20:43.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.21,0:20:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡朝倉同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.20,0:21:12.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是白河
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.53,0:21:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個白河會蹺課？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.10,0:21:16.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,琴…梨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.50,0:21:17.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.38,0:21:28.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她笑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.98,0:21:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像很開心的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.53,0:21:41.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被甩了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.07,0:21:45.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.17,0:21:48.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,心情為什麼會這麼好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.31,0:21:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能聽見他人的心聲嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.08,0:22:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,櫻花幫她實現了心願
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.78,0:22:06.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放心，琴梨一定沒問題的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.99,0:22:09.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說得也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.09,0:22:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我這麼做真的是對的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:30.01,0:22:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,預告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:31.11,0:22:34.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學長，我做了一個夢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:34.51,0:22:39.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小時候跟朝倉學長\N還有音夢學姊一起玩的夢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.42,0:22:45.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這代表在我身體裡面\N沈睡著真正美春的記憶對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:45.56,0:22:46.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美春
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.03,0:22:50.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要如此拘泥於\N真正美春的回憶呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:50.46,0:22:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們一起相處的時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.20,0:22:53.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這難道不算是回憶嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:53.83,0:22:55.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.14,0:22:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我知道…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:56.87,0:22:58.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，學長\N（#24  記憶之門）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:06.81,0:23:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從掌心滿溢灑落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:13.12,0:23:17.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有著眼淚顏色的花瓣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:18.79,0:23:24.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若是對風唱出搖曳的思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:24.40,0:23:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天會傳達到你身邊嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:32.34,0:23:38.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搜尋片段的記憶之線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:38.61,0:23:45.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是希望能在前方見到你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:45.12,0:23:52.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尋找小小腳印而徘徊的日子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.33,0:23:57.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算明知那裡什麼都沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:58.80,0:24:05.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為知道我是如此珍惜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:05.11,0:24:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使已經凋零\N仍能傲於曾經綻放而向前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:14.68,0:24:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如此永遠地…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:17.92,0:24:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將你的存在悄悄深藏於內心
